overview.en: DIYchain aims to make C2M (personal to manufacturer) a new point of business life through block chain technology and the actual situation of e-commerce industry, reduce the transaction cost of consumers, improve the production efficiency of manufacturers, let C2M point to point transaction into all aspects of life, let everyone trade, All things can be traded
overview.zh: DIYchain旨在通过区块链技术，结合电商行业的实际情况，打造C2M（个人到生产厂家）的全新点对点电商交易生活方式，降低消费者的交易成本，提高生产厂家的生产效率，让C2M点对点交易融入生活的方方面面，让人人皆可交易，物物皆可交易
